agentic-setup — third-party attributions
=========================================

The `adversarial-review` plugin adapts logic from:

    poteto/noodle  —  https://github.com/poteto/noodle
    MIT License, Copyright (c) 2026 Lauren Tan

Specifically: the critic-lens structure (Skeptic / Architect / Minimalist) and
the 5-step refute procedure of the adversarial-review skill are adapted from
noodle's adversarial-review skill. Only the IO / grounding layer is customized
(grounding source, subagent dispatch, soft-gate output). Per-file notes appear
in adversarial-review/skills/adversarial-review/.

